JOB POSTING // AUGUSTA, GA Creative Services Manager

DATE: June 9, 2017
TITLE: Creative Services Manager
LOCATION: Augusta, Georgia
DESCRIPTION: Beasley Media Group, Inc. is looking to hire a talented Creative Services manager to add to our Augusta, GA market. We are seeking a self-starter who is motivated and passionate about design and video. You will be working closely with the program directors, sales, marketing and web teams to deliver captivating designs and video that meets business needs. This dynamic professional will collaborate, design and execute projects including the creation of sales proposals, brand development, logo design, print/web event-marketing materials, social media campaigns, web ads/graphics, newsletter designs, film editing and event photography. The successful candidate will help with creation and production of customized market sales packages, create digital ads and products; be responsible for the overall appearance of Augusta station websites and social media accounts as well as film and edit event footage for sales-driven video projects. Must be a self-starter, with the ability to work in a fast-paced environment under minimum supervision.

Proven experience in logo design, advertising, print collateral, vehicle graphics and custom digital ad designs/web graphics
In-depth understanding of the creative process, concept development, color theory and typography
Ability to create cohesive visual campaign that translates across multiple platforms (print, websites, apps, social media)
High proficiency with all Adobe CC programs
Working knowledge of all Microsoft Office programs to include MS Word, MS PowerPoint, MS Excel, and MS Outlook
Must translate designs to working and editable PowerPoint files for sales use
Proven experience with videography and editing
