Beasley Broadcast Group Inc Overview



Website:

www.bbg.com

Locations:


                                                             Naples, FL 

                                                

Employees:
700




Founded:
N/A
CEO:
George G Beasley
Industry:

Radio Broadcasting Stations



Revenue:
$124,649,100





                                            At Naples, FL, you'll find radio broadcasting stations company Beasley Broadcast Group Inc's headquarters. It pulls in a yearly revenue of $124.6 million and employs 700 people. Beasley Broadcast Group Inc's unique nature and offerings are in high demand in the boutique market. The firm is run by CEO George G Beasley.
                                        









