The consistently rated #1 award winning morning show will be heard in both markets from 5:30am-10:30am Monday-Friday. READ MORE






Our Charlotte Market Shines Spotlight on Social Impact of Local Radio on Youth at Teen Conference
Beasley Media Charlotte recently partnered with local Teen Health Connection to host the Youth to Youth Southern States Conference Extreme Skill Workshop. Krista Stout and Chele Fassig (pictured) hosted a session entitled “Social Impact of Local Radio on Youth” with the group. READ MORE…






